      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_825E1530-1E46-0135-B5FF-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the title of the assignment you want to edit. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

