</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="edit_grading_type" data-step-uuid="13B15F3E-F548-4766-AE17-E66CD4752164">
    <h2 id="edit_grading_type" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Edit Grading Type</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/265/599/original/339d2ff7-bce5-4a1d-a085-9320e83ac799.png" srcset="" alt="Edit Grading Type" height="221" width="574">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_825F48A0-1E46-0135-B603-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Display Grade as</strong> drop-down menu and select how you would like to display the assignment grade. You can also <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-add-a-grading-scheme-in-a-course/ta-p/1054" target="_blank">manage grading schemes</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

