      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="grade_assignment" data-step-uuid="25AAC6FD-07B9-430E-83B1-43AAAB79C4FD">
    <h2 id="grade_assignment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Grade Assignment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/756/146/original/68e06537-c53d-4568-b92b-7bcd7edc2f85.png" srcset="" alt="Grade Assignment " height="248" width="236">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_826198A0-1E46-0135-B611-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In SpeedGrader, enter the point value for the assignment [1]. The point value will change to the name indicated in the grading scheme percentile range [2]. In this example, the point value (23 out of 25) is 92% and is expressed as an A-.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
